query:
SELECT 
  CONCAT(p.id, ',', 
         p.contractId, ',',
         p.propertyId, ',',
         p.paymentDate, ',',
         p.amountTotal, ',',
         p.principalAmount, ',',
         p.lateFeeAmount, ',',
         p.receivedBy, ',',
         p.channel, ',',
         IFNULL(REPLACE(p.memo, ',', ';'), '')) AS csv_row
FROM payments p
LEFT JOIN contracts c ON p.contractId = c.id
WHERE c.id IS NULL
ORDER BY p.propertyId, p.paymentDate;
